FBIS3-56080 "drsov009_v_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-009 Document Type:Daily Report 13 Jan 1994 Lithuania Government Decision on Soviet Secret Documents LD1301105394 Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service in Lithuanian 2200 GMT 12 Jan 94 LD1301105394 Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service Language: Lithuanian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Lithuanian Government declared at its closed meeting on Wednesday [12 January] as restricted all secret documents of the government institutions, the procuracy, courts, all structures of the Lithuanian Communist Party, offices, enterprises, and organizations during the period of Soviet occupation of Lithuania. The government press representative also announced that it was decided at the same meeting to abolish unilaterally visas to the citizens of Japan, Switzerland, Liechtenstein, and Italy.
